snippet.title: GALAXY BALLERINA - FULL PLAY (All endings)
snippet.description:
Embark on this delightful journey of camaraderie and creativity in Galaxy Ballerina, where every moment on stage is a chance to shine together. Join us as we delve into this heartwarming tale and uncover all the endings it has to offer, with timestamps conveniently provided below for your viewing pleasure.

📌 Timestamps:
00:00 - Galaxy Ballerina Full Play
03:24 - Normal End
05:15 - Bad End 1
07:14 - Bad End 2
10:18 - Bad End 3
14:01 - True End

🕹️ Want to experience the game yourself? Circus of GALAXY BALLERINA is available on ITCH.IO: https://miraongchua.itch.io/galaxy-ballerina

📺 More Indie Game Plays: Check out our other indie game plays on our Youtube playlist:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL-F0N8jK-1VycE00t9IWl1r2dKjhZ_bbt  

👍 If you enjoyed this video, please hit the like button and consider subscribing to our channel. Every recommendation and share supports us as a small indie channel. Don't forget to hit the bell icon to be notified when we post new videos. Thank you for watching!

#GalaxyBallerina #ShortStory #AllEndings #IndieGame #VisualNovel
